# Task Prompt Template

Use this file to define your task for Ralph Supreme. Copy to `PROMPT.md` and customize.

---

## Task

[Describe what you want to build or accomplish]

## Requirements

- [ ] Requirement 1
- [ ] Requirement 2
- [ ] Requirement 3

## Acceptance Criteria

When complete, the following must be true:
- Criteria 1
- Criteria 2
- All tests passing

## Completion Signal

When all requirements are met and acceptance criteria satisfied:
1. Output: `<promise>COMPLETE</promise>`
2. Include: `EXIT_SIGNAL: true`

---

## Example: REST API Task

```markdown
## Task

Build a REST API for managing todo items.

## Requirements

- [ ] CRUD endpoints: GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /todos
- [ ] Input validation on all endpoints
- [ ] Error handling with proper HTTP status codes
- [ ] SQLite database for persistence
- [ ] Unit tests with >80% coverage

## Acceptance Criteria

- All endpoints respond correctly to valid requests
- Invalid requests return appropriate error codes
- All tests pass
- README includes API documentation

## Completion Signal

When done: <promise>COMPLETE</promise>
EXIT_SIGNAL: true
```
